Stacklift - CloudFormation management tool
===============================================

Stacklift is a tool to manage CloudFormation stacks.

# Installation
```
pip install stacklift
```

# Usage
```
stacklift --help
```

# Development
```
pipenv install
PYTHONPATH=. pipenv run bin/stacklift
```


